snippet.title: NARUTO Powerful Shippuden (Nintendo 3DS) - The Ninja Way Trailer
snippet.description: The NARUTO Powerful Shippuden 3DS fighting game captures the essence of youth and packs an adorable punch as Rock Lee and Naruto Uzumaki embark on ninja adventures, facing familiar friends and foes along the way.
